[0m[49m[39m  493, 491[0m:[39m[49m **Performance benchmarks:**
[0m[49m[39m  494, 492[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  495, 493[0m:[39m[49m | Metric | Value |
[0m[49m[39m  496, 494[0m:[39m[49m |--------|-------|
